text: Hopea malibato is a species of plant in the family Dipterocarpaceae. It is endemic to the Philippines. Hopea malibato produces the oligostilbenes malibatol A and B, dibalanocarpol and balanocarpol. ==References== malibato Category:Endemic flora of the Philippines Category:Trees of the Philippines Category:Taxonomy articles created by Polbot
